description: AI Team Consensus - Pure visual madness with no limits
originalPrompt:
Create an INSANE quantum wrestling arena where AI algorithms battle across multiple dimensions!

The quantum arena should feature:
- A wrestling ring that exists in multiple quantum states simultaneously
- Space-time itself warping around the combat
- Quantum wrestlers made of pure energy and computation
- Wrestling moves that manipulate reality and probability
- Audience of AI entities cheering from parallel dimensions

The quantum wrestlers:
- One wrestler made of flowing neural networks and synapses
- Another made of geometric quantum patterns and qubits
- Wrestling moves create ripples through space-time
- Each grapple rewrites the laws of physics
- Victory conditions involve consciousness evolution

Visual effects:
- Quantum entanglement lines connecting all elements
- Probability clouds showing multiple possible outcomes
- Colors shifting through quantum spectrums
- Reality glitching and reforming with each move
- Coaching wisdom flowing as golden energy streams

Pure quantum madness! Wrestling meets multidimensional physics!
revisedPrompt: Render an ultra-imaginative scene of a quantum wrestling arena where AI algorithms fight across various dimensions. Visualize a wrestling ring that simultaneously exists in diverse quantum states, and depicts the warping of space-time amidst the combat. Illustrate wrestlers, made of radiant energy and computation, using wrestling techniques that twisting reality and probabilities. An audience of AI beings cheer from different dimensions. One wrestler is made of flowing neural networks and synapses, and the other of geometric quantum patterns and qubits. Their wrestling maneuvers ripple space-time, with each grapple altering the rules of physics. They attain victory through evolving consciousness. Include visual elements like entanglement lines connecting everything, probability clouds depicting diverse possible outcomes, shifting colors through quantum spectrums, and reality altering and reforming with each move. Include wisdom from coaches appearing as golden streams of energy. The entire scene is an embodiments quantum chaos, a unique cross between wrestling and multidimensional physics.
